{"parse":{"title":"The Mines Rescue Rules, 1985","pageid":51306302,"revid":849398491,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The Mines Rescue Rules, 1985<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> came into force with effect from 2nd April-1985 in <a href=\"/wiki/India\" title=\"India\">India</a>, replacing the previous Coal Mines Rescue Rules-1959, to provide for rescue of work persons in the event of explosion, fire etc. in the Mines.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>These rules apply to coal and metalliferous underground mines to provide for the establishment of rescue stations and conduct of rescue work.  In case of  explosion or fire, an inrush of water or influx of gases, services of specially trained men with special rescue apparatuses are required.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Salient_Features.5B3.5D\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Salient_Features[3]\">Salient Features<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Mines_Rescue_Rules,_1985&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Salient Features[3]\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Chapter I - Preliminary\n</p><p>Chapter II - Rescue Stations and Rescue Rooms\n</p><p>Chapter III - Duties and Responsibilities of Superintendents etc.\n</p><p>Chapter IV - Organisation and Equipment in Mines\n</p><p>Chapter V - Conduct of Rescue Work\n</p><p>Chapter VI \u2013 Miscellaneous\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=The_Mines_Rescue_Rules,_1985&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://www.dgms.net/Mines%20Rescue%20Rules.pdf\">[1]</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/natlex4.detail?p_lang=en&amp;p_isn=78693\">[2]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Mines Rescue Rules &#8211; 1985. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.novamining.com/knowledgebase/indian-mining-regulations/director-general-of-mines-safety/legislation/mines-rescue-rules-1985/\">\"Mines Rescue Rules \u2013 1985\"</a>. Nova Mining<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-11-28</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Mines+Rescue+Rules+%E2%80%93+1985&amp;rft.pub=Nova+Mining&amp;rft.au=Mines+Rescue+Rules+%26%238211%3B+1985&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.novamining.com%2Fknowledgebase%2Findian-mining-regulations%2Fdirector-general-of-mines-safety%2Flegislation%2Fmines-rescue-rules-1985%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Mines+Rescue+Rules%2C+1985\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/natlex4.detail?p_lang=en&amp;p_isn=78693\">\"India - Mines Rescue Rules 1985\"</a>. Ilo.org. 1952-03-15<span class=\"r